headline: Royal Caribbean, consumer confidence, Fed meeting: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Tuesday, October 28, including earnings results from companies like Visa (V), UnitedHealth Group (UNH), and Royal Caribbean Cruises (RCL); October's consumer confidence data; and the beginning of the Federal Reserve's October FOMC meeting, concluding on Wednesday with the latest decision around interest rates. headline: OpenTable Unveils Revamped Loyalty Program - OpenTable Regulars - Featuring New Savings and Better Benefits for Diners
summary: OpenTable, a global leader in restaurant technology, today launches its revamped loyalty program, OpenTable Regulars. For diners, the new program provides updated ways to redeem points on experiences and introduces enhanced status benefits. For restaurants, it helps drive repeat business.
